Kefir portable distribution package

Kefir portable distribution package provides standalone C17/C23 language
development toolchain, featuring statically-linked Kefir C17/C23 compiler, musl
libc standard library implementation, libatomic built from compiler_rt pieces,
and tools from GNU Binutils. The package is targeted for modern x86_64-based
Linux systems.

This package incorporates software from the following projects:
* Kefir C17/C23 compiler <https://sr.ht/~jprotopopov/kefir/>
* musl libc <https://musl.libc.org/>
* compiler_rt <https://compiler-rt.llvm.org/>
* GNU Binutils <https://www.gnu.org/software/binutils/>

Software licenses are available in share/licenses directory. For more details refer to
respective software project websites.